<taxonomicName id="4C8B6689A0B187B8319D36AFCEF91C5C" authorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" baseAuthorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Petrorhagia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Petrorhagia cretica" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cretica" status="comb. nov.">Petrorhagia cretica</taxonomicName>
