<typeStatus id="BC8D42FE98769DA2085015F66397DED4">Type</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6A38901E6FD1E7EB986D2B895D8C9033" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">not designated</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="3EE77E4FD5A99EB4CEC4B821633BFCE3" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" type="lectotype">
<paragraph id="A076F4D845F8D4D079DA1AB0EE8AF6A4" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Lectotype.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9840800B45C6E9E780B6F6882A49F55B" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">(designated by Davis in Notes Roy. Bot. Gard. Edinburgh 22: 164. 1957): locality, date and collector unknown, Herb. Linnaeus No. 580.4 (LINN!).</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6E9F091B05B2F77B56171CD23417A447" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">
<bibRefCitation id="79C253FC3C9939D00402B237C4A4B5A1" author="Davis, PH" journalOrPublisher="Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" pagination="163 - 171" refId="B30" refString="Davis, PH, 1957. New turkish species of Tunica, Velezia and Potentilla. Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh 22: 163 - 171" title="New turkish species of Tunica, Velezia and Potentilla." volume="22" year="1957">Davis (1957)</bibRefCitation>
had pointed out the name 
<taxonomicName id="B9F5D0FD9758BBD904BBF42BB5F56E28" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Tunica" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tunica cretica" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cretica">
<emphasis id="B719F14067412872000CA30692B9B545" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Tunica cretica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.) Fisch. &amp; C.A.Mey. (basionym: 
<taxonomicName id="A46C90034A03AB8CC66753A2D7E60DEF" authorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" baseAuthorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Saponaria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Saponaria cretica" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cretica">
<emphasis id="4A5F7FC4FB939380724DCCF0CAC036A4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Saponaria cretica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L.) had been misapplied, whereas in fact the type of the name (the specimen in LINN) is an annual species that was later named 
<taxonomicName id="4355CC3799C70BFDEBF0214E6B596E16" authorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" baseAuthorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Tunica" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Tunica pachygona" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pachygona">
<emphasis id="B2A272909327D6BEDA5FF08463EDFEF5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Tunica pachygona</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fisch. &amp; C.A.Mey. Accordingly, the correct name in 
<taxonomicName id="BAFE05F39B40915E00A1B9EC1E624FF2" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Dianthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Dianthus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D9E37F1E7ABA4DD7173C8D804B25A803" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Dianthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
would be 
<taxonomicName id="D1841A6268CE33E2D46F789084CBABDB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. pachygonus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pachygonus">
<emphasis id="0ACF80C6406EF4A876C47E793E920960" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">D. pachygonus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the new combination published here because the epithet of 
<taxonomicName id="CD0055FD97FE50E3367019AA61A92867" authorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Fassou &amp; Korotkova &amp; Nersesyan &amp; Koch &amp; Dimopoulos &amp; Borsch" baseAuthorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Saponaria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Saponaria cretica" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cretica">
<emphasis id="16D05D62425EA827D0F583D9ECD22BF8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Saponaria cretica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is preoccupied in 
<taxonomicName id="01A83E71CE40904EBBF93B5B70D91C15" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Dianthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Dianthus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A658D8767AF77407F3EE204976E4F2CF" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Dianthus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<taxonomicName id="B11ACFC5EC02D26DB553C23FCE05D978" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D. creticus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="creticus">
<emphasis id="DE1D2B1651D48F9AD315BE78004EA105" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">D. creticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Tausch. which is now treated as 
<taxonomicName id="CBDABA6F0F236A218BF3F298F7770FAE" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Dianthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Dianthus fruticosus subsp. creticus" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="fruticosus" subSpecies="creticus">Dianthus fruticosus subsp. creticus</taxonomicName>
(Tausch) Runemark.
</paragraph>
